snippet: A Minnesota man has been charged with immigration fraud for failing to disclose his military service in Bosnia-Herzegovina during the war there in the 1990s or crimes he committed including murder, U.S. authorities said on Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Minnesota Man Failed to Disclose Crimes in Bosnia: Indictment
headline.main: Minnesota Man Failed to Disclose Crimes in Bosnia: Indictment

lead_paragraph: A Minnesota man has been charged with immigration fraud for failing to disclose his military service in Bosnia-Herzegovina during the war there in the 1990s or crimes he committed including murder, U.S. authorities said on Wednesday.
